1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 24=

3
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,840
(Though fireworks are beautiful,)

4
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:08,319
(the most dazzling light
fades in a flash.)

5
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,920
(The most beautiful moments)

6
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:11,680
(never last.)

7
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,879
(They always leave you with regret.)

8
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,280
(Even if our love is)

9
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,200
(as brief as fireworks,)

10
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:19,319
(I will never regret it.)

11
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,640
(We won't be unlucky or short-lived!)

12
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:24,200
(May our love be as strong as gold,)

13
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,519
(and may we live to a hundred years.)

14
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:27,400
(Whether it's a story from a book)

15
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,959
(or the life of an ordinary couple,)

16
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,200
(I hope we)

17
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:34,200
(will have a beautiful
and lasting ending.)

18
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:39,439
(Look! A shooting star!)

19
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,400
(It's a good omen.)

20
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,439
(Let's make a wish!)

21
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:48,040
(I wish we won't be trapped by the past,)

22
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,920
(but keep moving forward.)

23
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,680
(I wish nothing would burden our hearts,)

24
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:56,040
(all that will come,
through time and distance.)

25
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:06,260
(Ling Xiao's Preferences
Liu Rushi's Preferences)

26
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:19,840
Your Highness,

27
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,319
this won't help anything.

28
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,000
The harder you try to forget
what you care about,

29
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:29,159
and the more it hurts you.

30
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,960
If I took the Oblivion Herb,

31
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:33,840
would all of this

32
00:02:35,159 --> 00:02:36,520
get better?

33
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,479
The greater the joy

34
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,599
you've had in love,

35
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:44,080
the deeper the pain when it's gone.

36
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,120
What's done is done.

37
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,199
You should try to let go, Your Highness.

38
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,080
Neither craving

39
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,520
nor fearing.

40
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:53,879
It was only after I met him

41
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,080
that I began to grow greedy.

42
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,639
No one had ever said

43
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,000
that they would give everything for me.

44
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:05,000
The more I desire,

45
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,879
the harder it is to walk away.

46
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,639
Loving so much
that I would give everything I have,

47
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,439
and fear of losing it all.

48
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,439
Loving so much
that I only want to cherish

49
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,719
and give.

50
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:24,039
Time cures everything.

51
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:27,680
It might ease the pain of parting

52
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,159
and the bitterness of memories.

53
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:40,560
Freeze!

54
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,280
It's been a while.

55
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,800
We meet again.

56
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,120
Who are you, really?

57
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,400
What have you done with Ke'er?

58
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,879
You lost memories again?

59
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,319
Come on.

60
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,479
You may not remember me,

61
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,800
but I know you so much.

62
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,480
You've got me tied up here.

63
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,319
What's your game?

64
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:22,199
My game?

65
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:25,079
Let me refresh your memory

66
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,600
about what you once were!

67
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:30,759
There was a princess

68
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,959
who saved a man,

69
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,959
brought him to the palace,

70
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,240
and in the end, that man

71
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,879
destroyed her kingdom and her family,

72
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,079
leaving her homeless and wandering.

73
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,120
Things just never go as we hope.

74
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,639
It breaks my heart.

75
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,000
Now tell me,

76
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,959
what should I call you now?

77
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,279
Jing Liuli?

78
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,360
Liu Rushi?

79
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,000
Or perhaps

80
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,360
I should address you as

81
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,319
Your Highness?

82
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:14,000
You've always been the noble princess,
haven't you?

83
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,680
You'll taste

84
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:17,600
a fate worse than death.

85
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,160
Take this!

86
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,199
Does it hurt?

87
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:29,040
Without this heart-wrenching pain,

88
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,240
how could you possibly remember

89
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,560
your despicable past?

90
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,199
(Mu Ruyi,)

91
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,319
(every moment with you)

92
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:40,439
(makes me feel disgusted to the core.)

93
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,480
(In this life,)

94
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,000
(the next,)

95
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,560
(and forever,)

96
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,519
(I will carry this hatred to my grave.)

97
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:55,040
(I never want to see you again.)

98
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,040
(Mu Ruyi!)

99
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,040
(Mother!)

100
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,680
(Mother!)

101
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,160
(Mother!)

102
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,680
(When I said
I don't care about the past,)

103
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:11,199
(I truly meant it.)

104
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:14,560
(Even if you've killed or hurt others,)

105
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,439
(whether you're a commoner)

106
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,879
(or the reigning king,)

107
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,720
(I only care about our future!)

108
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,800
(Do you understand?)

109
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,319
(Every person we loved)

110
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,600
(has been slaughtered
by each other's kin.)

111
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,759
(My mother was slain by your hands.)

112
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,360
(How could you ask me
to face you after that?)

113
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:32,040
(How could we ever speak of a future
with a clear conscience?)

114
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,560
(Everything about us)

115
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,160
(was a curse,)

116
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:37,439
(nothing but a mistake.)

117
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,879
(I never want to see you again,
for all eternity.)

118
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,040
You know Ling Xiao killed your mother,

119
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,040
so why do you keep changing
your identity

120
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,279
and staying by his side?

121
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:56,079
What is your purpose?

122
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,480
You keep silent?

123
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,120
Then just save it

124
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:03,360
for the grave!

125
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,240
Zhao Sisi!

126
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,800
What? You drop the act?

127
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,720
Is it all coming back?

128
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,800
Your time has come.

129
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,399
Zhao Sisi.

130
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,959
Say that again.

131
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,000
Love was never what you sought.

132
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:21,439
It was always your pathetic pride.

133
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,680
You've spent your life
as a slave to ambition,

134
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,639
a plaything of fame.

135
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,160
You're so lost in your sickness

136
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,839
that you can't even see
you've become a decoration.

137
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,439
When you wear a mask for too long,

138
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,519
it destroys both your heart and face.

139
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,319
Aside from empty titles
and a hollow shell,

140
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,600
you have nothing.

141
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,600
You're a dead person!

142
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,680
Nonsense!

143
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,279
Nonsense!

144
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,680
You're lying!

145
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,199
Then let's just see

146
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:49,120
who dies first!

147
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,839
Ling Xiao! Ling Xiao!

148
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,480
Ruyi!

149
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:09,079
Ke'er!

150
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,120
Ke'er.

151
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:28,600
Are you alright?

152
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,840
I remember everything now.

153
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:38,200
Whether good or bad,

154
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,039
painful,

155
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,399
or happy,

156
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,000
they are all the most important.

157
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:48,919
From the very beginning,

158
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,720
I have never doubted in my heart

159
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,360
the sincerity you had for me.

160
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,960
Just now, when I thought

161
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,440
I was about to die,

162
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,399
I realized

163
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,000
how much I love you,

164
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:06,960
how much I wanted to see you
one more time.

165
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:11,559
In this life,

166
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,879
we've borne too many burdens.

167
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,559
From now on,

168
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,480
I am no longer the King of Dongqing,

169
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,799
and you are no longer
the Princess of Xiling.

170
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,399
Let's be an ordinary couple,

171
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:31,559
side by side, forever.

172
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,279
Do you agree?

173
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,720
Together,

174
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,039
we'll find our future.

175
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,279
We leave the past behind

176
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,120
and only look to the future.

177
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,639
We never leave each other.

178
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,399
Ke'er.

179
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:55,660
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

180
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,399
Mo Shuo.

181
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,519
Is this a dream?

182
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,080
Sorry, Ke'er,

183
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,960
I came too late.

184
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:11,860
♪When we were fearless, you and me♪

185
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:16,580
♪Sometimes I wonder, in this life♪

186
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:21,100
♪Could there be another me somewhere♪

187
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,799
Ling Xiao!

188
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,039
Ling Xiao!

189
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:29,860
♪Longing for another you♪

190
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:33,460
♪If it truly exists in this world♪

191
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,360
Ling Xiao!

192
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,720
Ling Xiao!

193
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:37,559
Ling Xiao!

194
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,519
In this life,

195
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:46,240
I... I owe you too much.

196
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,320
No, you don't.

197
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,519
If

198
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:52,679
all this hatred could be dissolved,

199
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,039
I...

200
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,759
I am willing to...

201
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:58,480
I am willing to...

202
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,279
to...

203
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:07,240
Ling Xiao!

204
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,440
Ling Xiao!

205
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:09,679
- Ling Xiao!
- Ling Xiao!

206
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,639
Ling Xiao!

207
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,900
♪Even if just for a glance♪

208
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:21,900
♪Those years we shared
through joy and pain♪

209
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,240
(The one in my memories)

210
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,440
(and the one before my eyes,)

211
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:31,120
(which one is real?)

212
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,240
(True or false,)

213
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,799
(it no longer matters.)

214
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,759
(I've finally married you.)

215
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,080
(For all the years to come,)

216
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,639
(we shall stand side by side,)

217
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:48,240
(grow old together,)

218
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,559
(and protect each other forever.)

219
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,600
(Deal.)

220
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:58,980
♪This world holds too many regrets♪

221
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:03,180
♪You are the arrow
that pierces my yearning heart♪

222
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:08,140
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

223
00:12:08,700 --> 00:12:11,540
♪Even if just for a glance♪

224
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:17,700
♪Those years we shared
through joy and pain♪

225
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:23,380
♪When we were fearless, you and me♪

226
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:47,980
(Five years later)

227
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,200
Stop!

228
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:06,720
Don't run! Stop!

229
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,399
Jixiang, Ruyi,

230
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:12,200
come here.

231
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:15,840
Mother, who gave us our names?

232
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,840
It was your father.

233
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:21,000
Then, when will he come back
from the battlefield?

234
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,840
When you've grown up safe and sound,

235
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,000
he will return.

236
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,600
What kind of person is he?

237
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:31,000
Is he as harsh as you?

238
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,600
Your father is a brave

239
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,120
and kind man.

240
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:39,320
Does he miss us?

241
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,399
Indeed.

242
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,240
He misses us so much.

243
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,399
We miss him too.

244
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:11,840
Father!

245
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,639
Father!

246
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,519
Father!

247
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,279
(How I wish I could)

248
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,559
(see you one more time.)

249
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:22,159
(Even for just one second.)

250
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,279
(How I wish I could
see you one more time.)

251
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:27,639
(Even if only for a glance.)

252
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,519
(If there is a next life,)

253
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,639
(you must remember me.)

254
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,639
(Through our memories,
let's meet again soon.)

255
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,679
(Fearless and wild.)

256
00:14:40,639 --> 00:14:41,919
(You and I, back then.)

257
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,519
(If there is a next life,)

258
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,200
(let me be there first and protect you.)

259
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,519
(Through hardship and joy,)

260
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,320
(we never let it go.)

261
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:07,220
(The End)
